			<div
				class="absolute w-screen bottom-0 h-20 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#141B2F] to-transparent"
			>
			</div>
		</main>
		<section class="bg-[#141B2F] p-8">
			<div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="text-5xl font-bold md:place-self-end mb-10">
					About
				</h2>
				<p>
					I'm a University Student, a self-taught Full Stack Web
					Developer, and a technical-minded Entrepreneur.
				</p>
				<ul class="pl-4 list-disc">
					<li class="my-4">
						As a Student, I'm currently pursuing a Bachelor of
						Digital Design and Interactive Technologies at the IT
						University of Copenhagen.
					</li>
					<li class="my-4">
						As a Student, I'm currently pursuing a Bachelor of
						Digital Design and Interactive Technologies at the IT
						University of Copenhagen.
					</li>
					<li class="my-4">
						As a Student, I'm currently pursuing a Bachelor of
						Digital Design and Interactive Technologies at the IT
						University of Copenhagen.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="h-screen background-pattern relative pt-[20vh]">
			<div
				class="absolute w-screen top-0 h-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#141B2F] to-transparent"
			>
			</div>
			<div class="skills w-4/5 mx-auto">
				<img src="/assets/skills.png" alt="" />
				<p class="text-[#818CF8] font-semibold text-md my-5">
					What I can build
				</p>
				<h2
					class="text-3xl font-semibold md:place-self-end uppercase text-white"
				>
					Skills
				</h2>
				<p class="md:w-2/3 my-4">
					Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
